metadata.name: The Moon Ritual
metadata.description:
Genesis , Chapter 1 .

"The Moon ritual" is the seed of the entire collection. 
Here the Artist presents the mushroom wizard as he unleashes its magic to bring life and mystery to the forest with an esoteric ritual that wakes up ancient creatures and all things come alive.

Swamp gardens is a collection that presents a unique world in which the artist will expand his visual language to new heights, collect and join the mystic journey.
